{"sections":{"edbb72f8-c606-4713-aca3-24d4accd0081":{"type":"text-with-media","blocks":{"template--16196641292457__edbb72f8-c606-4713-aca3-24d4accd0081-image-1":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/PADDINGTON_EDM_HEADER_-_VISIT_GUIDE.png","mobile_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/PADDINGTON_EDM_HEADER_-_VISIT_GUIDE.png"}}},"block_order":["template--16196641292457__edbb72f8-c606-4713-aca3-24d4accd0081-image-1"],"settings":{"remove_spacing_top":false,"remove_spacing_bottom":true,"enable_newsletter_subscribe":false,"klaviyo_form_id":"","media_position":"right","media_position_mobile":"bottom","media_width":"7","content_position":"middleLeft","subheading":"<p><strong>COMMUNITY<\/strong><\/p>","title":"<p>A Day In Paddington: <em>Step Inside Our New Atelier & Explore Our Local Favourites<\/em><\/p>","description":"<p>Our new William Street Atelier was always intended to be more than just a physical boutique. It’s a portal to the NMJ experience - emblematic of our reverence for hand crafting and mindful consumption, and a place for our community to meet our passionate team (and each another).<\/p><p><\/p><p>As we open our doors, we’re excited to welcome you not only into our Atelier, but also to explore the vibrant and creative neighbourhood that surrounds us.<\/p><p><\/p><p>From dining to fashion and florals, we’ve compiled a guide to making the most of your day out in Paddington.<br\/><br\/>Catch a glimpse inside our new NMJ home and explore our visit guide below.<\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_style":"underline"}},"content_list_LGLhVN":{"type":"content-list","blocks":{"image_fQVVKP":{"type":"image","settings":{"apply_overlay":false,"devices":"mobile_desktop","content_position":"underLeft","subheading":"","title":"<p>For A Bite To Eat<\/p>","description":"<p>Begin your day with coffee and fresh produce at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/paddingtonalimentari\/?hl=en\">Paddington Alimentari <\/a>– a local favourite serving up artisanal bites and expertly poured brews. For lunch, you’ll find us at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/10williamst\/?hl=en\">10 William Street<\/a> for seasonal fare and natural wines (the pretzel with bottarga is a must), or try <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/barbettacucina\/?hl=en\" title=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/barbettacucina\/?hl=en\">Barbetta<\/a>, around the corner for authentic Italian dishes and the warmest hospitality.<\/p>","description_mobile":"<p>Begin your day with coffee and fresh produce at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/paddingtonalimentari\/?hl=en\">Paddington Alimentari <\/a>– a local favourite serving up artisanal bites and expertly poured brews. For lunch, you’ll find us at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/10williamst\/?hl=en\">10 William Street<\/a> for seasonal fare and natural wines (the pretzel with bottarga is a must), or try <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/barbettacucina\/?hl=en\" title=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/barbettacucina\/?hl=en\">Barbetta<\/a>, around the corner for authentic Italian dishes and the warmest hospitality.<\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_metaobject":"","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_2_metaobject":"","button_2_text":"","button_2_link":"","button_3_metaobject":"","button_3_text":"","button_3_link":"","button_style":"underline","include_no_media_border":false,"metaobject_autoplay":"","metaobject_loop":"","metaobject_apply_overlay":"","metaobject_content_position":"","metaobject_colour_style":"","metaobject_button_style":"","metaobject_devices":""}}},"block_order":["image_fQVVKP"],"name":"Content list","settings":{"grid_items_count":3,"grid_items_count_pocket":"1\/2","text_align":"center","subheading":"<p> <\/p>","title":"","description":"","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_2_text":"","button_2_link":"","button_style":"underline"}},"content_list_abG4G8":{"type":"content-list","blocks":{"image_4b